name: Summer Daydream pt2
description:
Sometimes the waves it's too short for us to ride it, all was suddenly gone, there's no time for lurking the so-called hope, hang on there, hold it tight, be bold.

The second issue, out of four issues from the Summer Daydreams series. Been shot using Diana plastic camera with Fujifilm Neopan Acros 100 120mm and animated with Adobe Photoshop.
